{
  "info": {
    "name": "Rescue Alert System ΓÇö Production",
    "description": "Production API reference for the Rescue Alert System.\n\n## Authentication\nAll endpoints (except Firebase Auth) require a Firebase ID Token as a Bearer token:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <firebase_id_token>\n```\n\n**Quick start:**\n1. Set `firebase_api_key`, `user_email`, and `user_password` in collection variables.\n2. Run **Firebase Auth ΓåÆ Sign In** ΓÇö it automatically saves the token to `firebase_token`.\n3. All other requests inherit the Bearer token from the collection.\n\nTokens expire after **1 hour**. Re-run Sign In to refresh.\n\n## Variables\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `base_url` | Production API base URL |\n| `firebase_api_key` | Firebase Web API key (from Firebase console ΓåÆ Project Settings) |\n| `user_email` | Email of the Firebase user to authenticate as |\n| `user_password` | Password of that Firebase user |\n| `firebase_token` | ID token ΓÇö **auto-set by Sign In request** |\n| `alert_id` | Alert ID for detail/update/delete requests |\n| `user_id` | UserProfile ID for detail/update/delete requests |\n| `group_id` | Group ID for detail/update/delete requests |\n| `message_id` | Message ID for detail/update/delete requests |\n| `notification_id` | Notification token record ID |\n\n## Notes\n- Django user accounts are created automatically on first authenticated request ΓÇö no separate registration step.\n- `sender` on messages and `user` on notifications are set automatically from the authenticated token; do not include them in request bodies.\n- `voice_file` uploads use `multipart/form-data`; do not set `Content-Type` manually ΓÇö Postman adds the boundary automatically.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://rescue-alert-system-malachim-badrachim.navonsimon.com",
      "description": "Production base URL"
    },
    {
      "key": "firebase_api_key",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Firebase Web API key ΓÇö Firebase console ΓåÆ Project Settings ΓåÆ General ΓåÆ Web API Key"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_email",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Email of the Firebase user to sign in as"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_password",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Password of the Firebase user"
    },
    {
      "key": "firebase_token",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Firebase ID token ΓÇö auto-set by the Sign In request. Valid for 1 hour."
    },
    {
      "key": "alert_id",
